last_episode_to_air.name: Grand Finale
last_episode_to_air.overview: The last three queens fight for the crown and the 100,000 Euro prize by performing RuPaul's hit song "Call Me Mother" and showing off their best looks on the runway.

name: Drag Race Germany
overview: Drag Race Germany is a German reality competition series, based on the original American series, RuPaul's Drag Race. The series is broadcast on MTV and Paramount+ in Germany, Austria, and Switzerland and on WOW Presents Plus internationally.

episodes.name: Willkommen in Deutschland
episodes.overview: 11 drag queens celebrate the start of Drag Race Germany with host Barbie Breakout and the resident judges: Gianni Jovanovic and Dianne Brill. Rapper Shirin David guest judges.

episodes.name: Fetish
episodes.overview: The second episode gets funny and sexy! After the Lip Sync battle, the first queen is eliminated.

episodes.name: Dragort: The Rusical
episodes.overview: The queens sing and dance for all they're worth in "Dragort" - the crime Rusical. Then on the runway, they present "Glitter-Party" looks.

episodes.name: Funny Shops
episodes.overview: There are a lot of reads in the mini-challenge, and 1,000 Angela Merkel looks on the runway.

episodes.name: Barbie Salesh
episodes.overview: The queens guess terms in "Drag Zack Zack", and the theme of the runway is "Rave Parade". The goodbye message on the mirror from the eliminated queen leaves a special mark.

episodes.name: Snatch Game
episodes.overview: The queens compete in a makeup mini challenge and play the Snatch Game. Dinner is served on the runway.

episodes.name: Poor But Sexy
episodes.overview: The queens create a rock star groupie look out of trash for the German Ball.

episodes.name: Comedy Roast
episodes.overview: The queens compete in a comedy roast and hairy affairs are on display.

episodes.name: Web Show
episodes.overview: The queens star in web shows and then present themselves as opera divas on the runway.

episodes.name: Dirndl Makeover
episodes.overview: The remaining queens give four superfans a drag-tastic dirndl makeover, and it will determine who makes it into the finals.
